                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6665" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1048</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8357 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">正中珠江的大溃败:特别代表人诉讼制度下的危局</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">An Overwhelming Defeat of Zhengzhong Pearl River: the Crisis of the Special Representative Litigation System</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">许文静，王玮炜，王则群，于欣平，伊丽帕提&#183;巴哈提</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国石油大学（北京）</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">广东正中珠江会计师事务所（特殊普通合伙）</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">正中珠江；审计失败；特别代表人诉讼制度</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Zhengzhong Pearl River；Audit Failure；Special Representative litigation system</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021年11月12日我国首例证券纠纷特别代表人诉讼案一审判决，正中珠江会计师事务所需承担康美药业因年报等虚假陈述侵权赔偿证券投资者损失24.59亿元的全部连带赔偿责任。至此，正中珠江声誉受损，客户、员工大规模出走，事务所名存实亡。正中珠江的“大溃败”描述了广东省第一大所正中珠江被卷入康美药业财务造假案件，事务所与审计人员在康美药业的年审项目中先后受到证监会行政处罚和法院的民事责任判决，特别在新《证券法》引入特别代表人诉讼制度后，事务所面临的审计责任发生的重大变化。本案例值得探讨的问题有：（1）正中珠江应如何保障审计质量以规避审计失败；（2）特别代表人诉讼制度在哪些方面做出了根本变化，该变化对会计师事务所承担的审计责任带来哪些影响；（3）特别代表人诉讼制度对审计行业带来了怎样的冲击，审计行业应如何推进未来的可持续发展。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">On November 12, 2021, China&#39;s first special representative case due to securities disputes was decided at the first instance trial. According to the court&#39;s judgment, Zhengzhong Pearl River certified public accountants shall bear joint and several liabilities for the loss of 2.459 billion yuan to securities investors due to the false statement of Kangmei pharmaceutical&#39;s annual report. At this point, the reputation of the Zhengzhong Pearl River was damaged, customers and employees fled on a large scale, and the firm was in name only. “An overwhelming defeat of Zhengzhong Pearl River” describes Zhengzhong Pearl River, the largest accounting firm in Guangdong province, was involved in the financial fraud case of Kangmei Pharmaceutical; The firm and auditors have been subject to administrative punishment by the CSRC and civil liability judgment by the court due to the annual report audit project of Kangmei pharmaceutical; especially the audit risk and responsibility have been changed greatly after the introduction of special representative litigation system in the new securities law. The problems worth discussing in this case include :(1) How to guarantee audit quality to avoid audit failure for Zhengzhong Pearl River; (2) What are the fundamental changes in the litigation system of the special representative? the impact of the changes on the audit responsibility of the accounting firm;(3) What impacts the special representative litigation system have brought to the audit industry, and how the audit industry should promote its sustainable development in the future.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《审计理论与实务》、《审计学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">审计质量；审计责任；审计职业道德；职业责任保险</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
